definitions.definition: An animal of the phylum Echinodermata , comprising radially symmetric , spiny-skinned marine animals including seastars , sea urchins , sea cucumbers , crinoids , and sand dollars .

main_definition: An animal of the phylum Echinodermata , comprising radially symmetric , spiny-skinned marine animals including seastars , sea urchins , sea cucumbers , crinoids , and sand dollars . [from 19th c.]
